{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/1438_Apeiron.jpg?t=1737586449\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the breathtaking world of <i>Limitless (&quot;Formerly known as Apeiron&quot;)</i>, an open-world, third-person, story-driven action RPG set in the mystical Realm of Eternity. Experience a richly crafted high-fantasy universe filled with danger, discovery, and dynamic gameplay. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/600x22-main-center-divider.png?t=1737586449\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build Your Dream Team of Heroes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lead a squad of four remarkable companions, each with their own strengths, skills, and customizable gear. Strategically swap between characters in real-time to overcome challenges, solve mysteries, and turn the tide of battle in your favor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/TOFHAlchemist_-_Unreal_Editor_2024-05-29_16-30-58__1___2_.gif?t=1737586449\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u00a0Master the Art of Combat with Weapon Stances\u00a0</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Revolutionize your battles with our cutting-edge weapon stance system. Instantly switch between powerful combat styles to counter enemies, adapt to changing battlefields, and unleash devastating attacks that will leave your foes in awe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/TOFHAlchemist_-_Unreal_Editor_2024-05-29_16-30-58__1___3_.gif?t=1737586449\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Conquer Puzzles with Elemental Power</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage your mind and creativity with clever puzzles that demand mastery of the elements. Unlock hidden paths, discover ancient treasures, and bring light to the darkest corners of the Realm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/unnamed__4_.gif?t=1737586449\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Unleash the Power of Dynamic Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience combat like never before with fluid, multi-layered mechanics that allow for limitless creativity. Harness the power of elemental abilities, devastating combos, and unique strategies to dominate your enemies and carve your own path to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/unnamed__4_5.gif?t=1737586449\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/unnamed__3_1.gif?t=1737586449\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/unnamed__5_.gif?t=1737586449\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/600x22-main-center-divider.png?t=1737586449\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong> </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Dive into a Decade of Legendary Storytelling</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in a tale of epic proportions, meticulously crafted over ten years. Follow Dayton, the wielder of an ancient relic, as he battles the interdimensional Ravi army and uncovers the secrets of the Elemental Crystal Fragments in a race to save the Realm from total annihilation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/unnamed31-ezgif.com-cut__1_.gif?t=1737586449\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/TOFHAlchemist___2025-01-10_15-23-54__2_.gif?t=1737586449\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>The Journey Awaits</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The once-peaceful Realm of Eternity stands on the brink of destruction. As Dayton, forge alliances with warriors, politicians, and cultural icons to challenge the Ravi and reclaim the world\u2019s destiny. The ultimate battle looms in the fabled Garden of Eden\u2014will you be the hero who restores balance?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737586449","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/page.bg.jpg?t=1737586449","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/4ef6e186ca2cdd0c5f9ea69b3bdb1a413da84472/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737586449","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/4ef6e186ca2cdd0c5f9ea69b3bdb1a413da84472/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737586449","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3113840,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2251920/extras/1438_Apeiron.jpg?t=1737586449\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the breathtaking world of <i>Limitless (&quot;Formerly known as Apeiron&quot;)</i>, an open-world, third-person, story-driven action RPG set in the mystical Realm of Eternity. Experience a richly crafted high-fantasy universe filled with danger, discovery, and dynamic gameplay. </p><p class=\"bb_paragr